description: Redevelopment by the erection of 4 new blocks. Block A 5 storeys high, Blocks B & C 9 storeys and block D part 11 & part 13 storeys with a new canal basin, towpath and associated car parking. Use of the new blocks as 83 one-bedroom, 104 two-bedroom, and 14 three-bedroom residential units and 2 units for Class A1/A3/B1 or D2 use.
